{"about_the_game":"<i>\u201cLovecraft would surely be pleased seeing that his writings have inspired even text-based games to such an elaborate extent. Travelyan Home proves that eye candy is not required for a good scare.\u201d - I DO BEST</i><br><br>Follow the path of a lost soul pacing the grounds of an old and mysterious mansion as he seeks the answers of what brought him there.<br><br>Introducing a unique investigation system to discover clues, items and hidden texts that progress the story and help the player uncover the secrets of the mansion.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258070/extras/gif1.gif?t=1591428457\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover what lies beyond the veil</h2><br>An absorbing storyline inspired by the masterful works of Poe, Lovecraft, Ashton Smith and others with over 160,000 written words to be discovered in descriptions, clues and hidden journals. <i>(Optional accessible font included)</i><br><br>*Over 50 rooms to explore and investigate with unique settings, intrigues and characters.<br><br>*Four characters to select from with unique backgrounds and skills<br><br>*6 different endings based on the player\u2019s decisions throughout the game<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258070/extras/gif2.gif?t=1591428457\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose your story</h2><br>Unique game mechanics combining role-playing and survival horror elements, offering a tactical gameplay where every action matters.<br><br>* Randomised events and encounters to solve, making every playthrough a unique experience<br><br>*A card-based item system with over 70 different items to help the player face the perils of the forgotten home<br><br>*A fast-paced combat system that tests your skills against what lurks in the shadows<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258070/extras